	<h1 class="title">「酸汤鱼经济学」为何防止踩踏不应该靠限制人流</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/3891/small/3891.jpg?1418027288" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">酸汤鱼</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-01-03 16:48:58 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/4891/medium/4891.jpeg?1436674443" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="4891" data-title="《「酸汤鱼经济学」为何防止踩踏不应该靠限制人流》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/4891/medium/4891.jpeg?1436674443" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/4891.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
	<div class="share-bd clearfix">
